261
00:20:16,690 --> 00:20:18,540
Whatever.

262
00:20:21,350 --> 00:20:24,470
- But, you know...
- What?

263
00:20:24,470 --> 00:20:27,190
What do you like about Choi Woo Seung?

264
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:29,720
Why are you curious about it?

265
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:33,610
No. I mean there must be a reason somehow.

266
00:20:33,610 --> 00:20:37,040
I don't have a reason. I just like her.

267
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:38,670
You can't like a person without a reason in this world.

268
00:20:38,670 --> 00:20:40,880
I don't have a reason to like her.

269
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:43,120
I like her because I like her.

270
00:20:49,990 --> 00:20:52,010
Hey!

271
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:54,920
