272
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:57,260
Then, hold on to that side.

273
00:20:58,980 --> 00:21:01,080
Who do you take after that you're...?

274
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:06,000
Aigoo, forget it. I'd be digging my own grave.

275
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,760
Give it to me.

276
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:25,450
