277
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:29,130
Yes. I'll be right there.

278
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:41,130
Okay. This should be enough. Where did you learn to create and organize a presentation so well?

279
00:21:41,130 --> 00:21:45,500
Ah. I used to do a lot of group presentations, myself.

280
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:49,010
