00:28:31,560 --> 00:28:33,490
♫ Tonight  ♫

371
00:28:35,970 --> 00:28:40,700
He's not here again? How come there are more times when the management office doesn't have a CEO?

372
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:52,170
What?

373
00:28:52,190 --> 00:28:54,310
"Anyway, I will win this in the end. Choi Woo Seung."

