380
00:29:34,230 --> 00:29:37,030
Choi Woo Seung. If you're going to shower, you can use it first.

381
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:38,860
Okay.

382
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:49,330
Wow!

383
00:29:50,120 --> 00:29:52,870
