00:30:20,260 --> 00:30:23,210
I said it's not like that.

391
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:27,560
What on earth are you doing here?

392
00:30:32,140 --> 00:30:33,890
Here.

393
00:30:33,890 --> 00:30:36,370
You took my handphone instead of yours by mistake earlier.

394
00:30:36,370 --> 00:30:38,000
What?

395
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:42,710
Ah, wait a moment.

396
00:30:42,710 --> 00:30:45,840
Hey, Choi Woo Seung! How come you're not answering the phone? What is this?

397
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:48,990
